Dialogue: 2,0:09:22.29,0:09:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯 加油…
Dialogue: 2,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不對 給我去學校啊
