Dialogue: 2,0:17:39.49,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那些羨煞旁人的事 對我們來說是重要的交流方式
Dialogue: 2,0:17:45.00,0:17:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我才不管這些常識
Dialogue: 2,0:17:50.21,0:17:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你們倒是讓我也看看那些羨煞旁人的事啊
Dialogue: 2,0:17:55.13,0:17:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看你個鬼啊
Dialogue: 2,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}小司
Dialogue: 2,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}老公
Dialogue: 2,0:18:00.43,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 2,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那個…
Dialogue: 2,0:18:05.52,0:18:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}早安
Dialogue: 2,0:18:07.81,0:18:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯…早安
Dialogue: 2,0:18:15.15,0:18:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}昨…昨晚真是火熱呢
Dialogue: 2,0:18:18.41,0:18:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不…不是 並沒有到那種地步
Dialogue: 2,0:18:19.99,0:18:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 2,0:18:20.82,0:18:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真的 真的啊
Dialogue: 2,0:18:21.99,0:18:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}小司你和她說了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 2,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}早安 千歲
Dialogue: 2,0:18:31.00,0:18:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太陽曬屁股了哦
Dialogue: 3,0:18:34.21,0:18:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哎呀哎呀 今天的睡姿也是如此性感呢
Dialogue: 3,0:18:42.55,0:18:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}千歲 早上啦
Dialogue: 3,0:18:45.81,0:18:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以說你為什麼要把臉貼這麼近啊
Dialogue: 3,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因為你完全不起床啊
Dialogue: 3,0:18:52.02,0:18:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然後…
Dialogue: 3,0:18:53.82,0:18:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我會起床的 離我遠點
Dialogue: 3,0:19:01.62,0:19:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那我來幫你換衣服吧
Dialogue: 3,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}笨蛋笨蛋 你把手往哪伸啊
Dialogue: 3,0:19:07.87,0:19:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我幫你脫衣服哦
Dialogue: 3,0:19:09.92,0:19:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}誰要你幫啊
Dialogue: 3,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}別害羞嘛
Dialogue: 3,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}這並非性騷擾
Dialogue: 3,0:19:14.79,0:19:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}這女僕 只是個天然色
Dialogue: 3,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}話說剛才我聽說了哦
Dialogue: 3,0:19:24.26,0:19:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}星空和小司昨晚好像非常火熱哦
Dialogue: 3,0:19:29.94,0:19:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什麼意思
Dialogue: 3,0:19:33.10,0:19:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不 剛才…
Dialogue: 3,0:19:34.81,0:19:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我去澡堂洗澡的時候
Dialogue: 3,0:19:37.44,0:19:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}碰巧聽到他們在說這些
Dialogue: 3,0:19:39.69,0:19:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你早上還去那裡洗澡嗎
Dialogue: 3,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不…不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 3,0:19:45.24,0:19:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}反…反正他們是夫妻 做這些不是很正常嗎…
Dialogue: 3,0:19:48.66,0:19:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}這些指的是什麼事？
Dialogue: 3,0:19:51.96,0:19:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}請告訴我他們做了哪些火熱的事
Dialogue: 3,0:19:56.29,0:19:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不不不 又太近了
Dialogue: 3,0:19:59.21,0:20:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就是在床上牽手擁抱那檔子事啊
Dialogue: 3,0:20:04.30,0:20:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是我平時對千歲做的那些事嗎
Dialogue: 3,0:20:06.76,0:20:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}能不能說人話
Dialogue: 3,0:20:08.64,0:20:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}比起那些
Dialogue: 3,0:20:10.98,0:20:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}更加激烈
Dialogue: 3,0:20:16.23,0:20:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}激烈…
Dialogue: 3,0:20:18.73,0:20:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}簡單來說
Dialogue: 3,0:20:20.90,0:20:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就是夫妻關係和睦吧
Dialogue: 3,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是啊
Dialogue: 3,0:20:26.28,0:20:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯嗯 關係和睦是好事
Dialogue: 3,0:20:30.79,0:20:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我和歐羅拉也是關係和睦的好朋友？
Dialogue: 3,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}算…算是吧
Dialogue: 3,0:20:37.79,0:20:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那麼
Dialogue: 3,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今晚就牽著手一起睡吧
Dialogue: 3,0:20:45.68,0:20:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也行…
Dialogue: 3,0:20:49.64,0:20:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}開玩笑的 玩笑玩笑
Dialogue: 3,0:20:52.81,0:20:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那麼 晚安啦
Dialogue: 3,0:20:58.44,0:20:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}魔性的女人
Dialogue: 3,0:21:07.82,0:21:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}明…明天也要早起 差不多該睡了呢
Dialogue: 3,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是…是啊
Dialogue: 3,0:21:15.37,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}回頭讓小要看到我們沒睡好
Dialogue: 3,0:21:17.21,0:21:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不知道她又會說什麼
Dialogue: 3,0:21:20.80,0:21:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是啊
