Dialogue: 3,0:21:42.36,0:21:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}晚安之吻呢
Dialogue: 3,0:21:45.61,0:21:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所…所以說那樣就又會…
