Dialogue: 3,0:22:54.06,0:22:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天也宛如初戀一般
Dialogue: 3,0:22:59.02,0:23:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}兩人牽著手
